---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout title="About DevDocs" description="About the DevDocs documentation site">
  <main class="about-page">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[
        { label: 'About', href: '/about' }
      ]} />
      
      <h1>About DevDocs</h1>
      
      <p class="intro">
        DevDocs is a comprehensive documentation site designed to help developers master modern web development technologies through clear, concise, and practical guides.
      </p>
      
      <section class="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Our mission is to provide high-quality, accessible documentation for developers at all skill levels. We believe that clear and comprehensive documentation is essential for learning and mastering new technologies.
        </p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="content">
        <h2>Our Content</h2>
        <p>
          DevDocs offers articles covering a wide range of development topics, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Frontend Development</strong>: JavaScript, CSS, frameworks like Vue.js and React</li>
          <li><strong>Backend Development</strong>: Node.js, Express, databases, API design</li>
          <li><strong>DevOps</strong>: Server configuration, deployment, CI/CD pipelines</li>
          <li><strong>Developer Tools</strong>: Git, Chrome DevTools, VS Code, testing frameworks</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section class="contribution">
        <h2>Contribute</h2>
        <p>
          DevDocs is an open-source project and we welcome contributions from the community. Whether it's fixing a typo, adding a new article, or suggesting improvements, we appreciate all contributions.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="/contribute" class="cta-button">Learn how to contribute</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #7c3aed;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>